#. type: expansion
#: sections/variants.tex:205
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"  Based on the Scenario's Difficulty Level, take a number of \\pagelink{Stack Tokens}{Stack Tokens} and place them randomly on up to four different Creature Bank unit cards:\n"
"  \\begin{itemize}\n"
"    \\item \\textbf{Easy}: 1 token\n"
"    \\item \\textbf{Normal}: 2 tokens\n"
"    \\item \\textbf{Hard}: 3 tokens\n"
"    \\item \\textbf{Impossible}: 4 tokens\n"
"  \\end{itemize}\n"
"  \\end{multicols*}"
msgstr ""
"  Abhängig von der gewählten Szenario-Schwierigkeit, ziehe eine Anzahl an \\pagelink{Stack Tokens}{Rudelmarkern} und platziere zufällig je einen auf verschiedene Einheitenkarten:\n"
"  \\begin{itemize}\n"
"    \\item \\textbf{Leicht}: 1 Marker\n"
"    \\item \\textbf{Normal}: 2 Marker\n"
"    \\item \\textbf{Experte}: 3 Marker\n"
"    \\item \\textbf{Unmöglich}: 4 Marker\n"
"  \\end{itemize}\n"
"  \\end{multicols*}"

#. type: multicols*
#: sections/variants.tex:212
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"{2}\n"
"  \\begin{expansion}{navalbattles}\n"
"  After Combat, return all Creature Bank units back to the Creature Bank units cards pile.\n"
"  If you win, you claim the Creature Bank's reward, as well as an additional reward for the Stacked units you defeated.\n"
"\n"
msgstr ""
"{2}\n"
"  \\begin{expansion}{navalbattles}\n"
"  Sortiere nach dem Kampf alle Kreaturenbank-Einheitenkarten zurück in ihr Deck.\n"
"  Nach einem Sieg erhältst du die Belohnungen der Kreaturenbank, sowie eine zusätzliche Belohnung für besiegte Rudeleinheiten.\n"
"\n"

#. type: multicols*
#: sections/variants.tex:217
#, fuzzy, no-wrap
#| msgid ""
#| "  \\subsection*{\\pagetarget{Stack Tokens}{Stack Tokens}}\n"
#| "  Each Stack Token modifies a unit's statistic in the following way: +1~\\svg{attack}, +1~\\svg{defense}, +1~\\svg{health_points}, or +2~\\svg{initiative}.\n"
#| "  Furthermore, each unit with a Stack Token is now a \\textbf{Stacked unit}, which is similar to reinforced Faction units: when it takes damage equal to or greater than its \\svg{health_points}, instead of removing the unit card from the Combat Board, discard the Stack Token from that unit and deal any leftover damage, deducting it from the new \\svg{health_points}.\n"
#| "  Creature Bank units without a Stack Token are defeated normally.\n"
#| "\n"
msgid ""
"  \\subsection*{\\pagetarget{Stack Tokens}{Stack Tokens}}\\index{Stacked Units}\n"
"  Each Stack Token modifies a unit's statistic in the following way: +1~\\svg{attack}, +1~\\svg{defense}, +1~\\svg{health_points}, or +2~\\svg{initiative}.\n"
"  Furthermore, each unit with a Stack Token is now a \\textbf{Stacked unit}, which is similar to reinforced Faction units: when it takes damage equal to or greater than its \\svg{health_points}, instead of removing the unit card from the Combat Board, discard the Stack Token from that unit and deal any leftover damage, deducting it from the new \\svg{health_points}.\n"
"  Creature Bank units without a Stack Token are defeated normally.\n"
"\n"
msgstr ""
"  \\subsection*{\\pagetarget{Stack Tokens}{Rudelmarker}}\n"
"  Jeder Rudelmarker modifiziert die Einheitenstatistiken entweder um +1~\\svg{attack}, +1~\\svg{defense}, +1~\\svg{health_points}, oder +2~\\svg{initiative}.\n"
"  Weiterhin gilt diese Einheit nun als Rudeleinheit, was dem Verstärken von Fraktionseinheiten ähnelt: Anstatt die Einheitenkarte vom Kampfspielplan zu entfernen, wenn der Schaden die Anzahl der LP erreicht oder übersteigt, wird zuerst der Rudelmarker entfernt und überzähliger Schaden (falls vorhanden) auf die neuen LP angerechnet.\n"
"  Kreaturenbank-Einheiten ohne Rudelmarker werden wie üblich besiegt.\n"
"\n"

#. type: multicols*
#: sections/variants.tex:224
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"  \\begin{multicols}{4}\n"
"    \\centering\n"
"    \\includegraphics[width=1.2\\linewidth]{\\images/stack-token-attack.png}\n"
"    \\includegraphics[width=1.2\\linewidth]{\\images/stack-token-defense.png}\n"
"    \\includegraphics[width=1.2\\linewidth]{\\images/stack-token-hp.png}\n"
"    \\includegraphics[width=1.2\\linewidth]{\\images/stack-token-initiative.png}\n"
"  "
msgstr ""

#. type: multicols*
#: sections/variants.tex:231
#, fuzzy, no-wrap
#| msgid ""
#| "  \\subsection*{Gained Stacked Units}\n"
#| "  Some rewards allow you to gain a Stacked Creature Bank unit card.\n"
#| "  Track which of your units are Stacked by whatever means is comfortable, e.g.~by remembering it or by placing a Token or Cube on it.\n"
#| "  Whenever your Stacked unit goes to a Combat, draw a random Stack Token and place it on that unit.\n"
#| "  After Combat, note whether the unit is still Stacked (for future Combats), then return the Stack Token to the pile.\n"
#| "  \\end{expansion}\n"
#| "  \\includegraphics[width=\\linewidth]{\\art/energy_elemental.jpg}"
msgid ""
"  \\subsection*{Gained Stacked Units}\n"
"  Some rewards allow you to gain a Stacked Creature Bank unit card.\n"
"  Track which of your units are Stacked by whatever means is comfortable, e.g.~by remembering it or by placing a Token or Cube on it.\n"
"  Whenever your Stacked unit goes to a Combat, draw a random Stack Token and place it on that unit.\n"
"  After Combat, note whether the unit is still Stacked (for future Combats), then return the Stack Token to the pile.\n"
"\n"
msgstr ""
"  \\subsection*{Rudeleinheiten erhalten}\n"
"  Einige Belohnungen erlauben es dir, eine Kreaturenbank-Rudeleinheit zu erhalten.\n"
"  Behalte die Einheitenkarte und markiere sie auf eine für dich komfortable Weise, um sie als Rudeleinheit auszuweisen, z.B.~durch Platzieren eines Fraktionswürfels.\n"
"  Sobald deine Rudeleinheit in den Kampf zieht, ziehe zufällig einen Rudelmarker und platziere ihn auf der Einheit.\n"
"  Ist deine Einheit nach dem Kampf immer noch eine Rudeleinheit, markiere sie (für zukünftige Kämpfe) erneut und mische den Rudelmarker zurück in den Vorrat.\n"
"  \\end{expansion}\n"
"  \\includegraphics[width=\\linewidth]{\\art/energy_elemental.jpg}"

