#| "\\vspace{2em}\n"
#| "\\begin{expansion}{battlefield}\n"
#| "  As an \\textbf{optional rule}, you can use the Battlefield Board for combats between players in regular games.\n"
#| "  You can also use it for Neutral Combats, though this is not recommended.\n"
#| "  Refer to the official Battlefield rulebook for the rule changes regarding this combat type.\n"
#| "\n"
msgid ""
"  \\vspace{2em}\n"
"  \\begin{expansion}{battlefield}\n"
"  As an \\textbf{optional rule}, you can use the \\textbf{Battlefield Board} for combats between players in regular games.\n"
"  You can also use it for Neutral Combats, though this is not recommended.\n"
"  Refer to the \\pagelink{Battlefield Combat}{Battlefield section} for the rule changes regarding this Combat type.\n"
"\n"
msgstr ""
"\\vspace{2em}\n"
"\\begin{expansion}{battlefield}\n"
"  Als \\textbf{optionale Regel} kannst du den Schlachtfeld-Spielplan für Kämpfe zwischen Spielern in regulären Spielen verwenden.\n"
"  Dies kannst du auch für neutrale Kämpfe tun, wird aber nicht empfohlen.\n"
"  Die Regeländerungen finden sich im offiziellen Regelheft dieser Erweiterung.\n"
"\n"

